name: Cubeist Warfair HTML Version
description: This is Cubeist Warfair! a Game where you are a Cube and have to kill other Cubes in a Multiplayer Experience. with Guns, Swords, and a Grappling Hook? so yeah that's Cubeist Warfair. Cubeist Warfair, Coming Soon, To PC/Itch.io (Game is now Playable but The Update/Alpha only Contains: In Game Multiplayer, In Game Grappling Hook, In Game Gun, Main Menu, Room Creator/Searcher Menu, In Room Lobby Menu, And also Customize Color Settings)
